Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}本片开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我跟女儿住在公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}生活虽然不富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}但也算幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}先生三年前去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}他生前有过许多投资
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}所以留下一些资产给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}你应该持有股票吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}可以聊聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}聊什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}想见面直接说明 可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我现在准备晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}要是这时找人商量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}也就不会发生那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}谢谢你肯抽出空来跟我面谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}要商量什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}请把你的股份转让给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我会以高于市价向你购买
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我不是只要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}这条件很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}这时我先生留下的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我正要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}太太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}你说股票是羁绊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}很重视家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}改变做法方式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}步美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}步美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}股票卖给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:06:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}步美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}步美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}你女儿在哭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}说什么羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}眼前的亲人比较重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}你不卖股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}跟他没关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}停不下来来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}都是你妈的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}看这
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}第一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}继续揉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}同时试试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}含啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}嘴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}还有一根
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}变的很坦白咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}快签
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}随你想做都行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}跟说好的不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}步美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}你房间的正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}我知道你很有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}谁叫你先生要买股票
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}步美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}好好看着
